with the sodium chloride

126
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:36,072
to produce calcium chloride.

127
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:41,554
Because calcium chloride is a
conductor, the little lamp lights.

128
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:50,074
